{"tid":2049353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨軍：呼籲明天市民盡量留在家中 唔係有咩冬瓜豆腐就唔好啦","createTime":"2020-06-03T11:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T12:44:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"137fda03469e4da89767fbecdd866d71b58b024e","tid":2049353,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"警方呼籲明天市民盡量留在家中<br />\n03.06.2020 19:26<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，早前接獲團體通知擬於明天在港島和九龍分別舉行公眾集會，經風險評估後，認為有關公眾集會屬人多聚集的高危活動，已向主辦方發出「禁止公眾集會通知」，公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會亦駁回上訴。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，香港仍出現本地感染個案，鑑於病毒性質和專家的建議，市民應盡量減少社交接觸和保持適當的社交距離，禁止群組聚集的規例仍然生效，呼籲市民應盡量留在家中，避免到人多的地方和參與受禁群組聚集。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298595&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1298595%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=f17fe166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1298595&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"cdf23737512e1b184cca559f9c37c6a3fe6c84c6","tid":2049353,"uid":54721,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"唔駛返工咩"},{"pid":"32465e907767a9296b981cc49d2fb277f16caf08","tid":2049353,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:37:08.000Z","msg":"先禮後兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94e0170e4a2565166aaaeb41878347f38592af5","tid":2049353,"uid":277339,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"禁止返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a2a2fa12323e05cbc32d786c173f013c251605","tid":2049353,"uid":115579,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32465e907767a9296b981cc49d2fb277f16caf08","tid":2049353,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:37:08.000Z","